articles.title: JU signs MoU with M/S ICT Academy for ICT related collaborations
articles.description: Excelsior Correspondent JAMMU, Sept 29: The University of Jammu signed a Memorandum of Understanding (MoU) with M/S ICT Academy, Chennai, Tamil Nadu, marking a significant step towards enhancing skill development, industry-relevant training, and academic research. The signing ceremony took place in the virtual presence of Satish Sharma, Minister for Food, Civil Supplies & Consumer Affairs, Transport, Science & Technology, Information Technology, Youth Services & Sports, and ARI & Trainings, and Prof Umesh Rai, Vice Chancellor, University of Jammu.
